{
  "id": "adv_card_rei_06_02",
  "title": "一ノ瀬怜",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_toffice_noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\nこれを見てもらえますか",
      "startTime": 2.2,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2066.6666667,
          "startTime": 4.2666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "これは……ダンス大会のパンフレット？\nこの大会がどうかしたのか？",
      "startTime": 8.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "そのダンス大会に出場したいので\n許可をいただきたいんです",
      "startTime": 13.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "怜はアイドルになってから、こういった大会には一度も\n出場していないよな？　それが急にどうしたんだ？",
      "startTime": 19.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "……その大会にエリカが出場するんです",
      "startTime": 23.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "ここで勝って、アイドルを馬鹿にした彼女に\nアイドルは凄いんだってことを示したいんです",
      "startTime": 31.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "この間のことで腹を立てる気持ちも分かるが\n何もそこまでしなくても……",
      "startTime": 38,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "私のことを悪く言われただけなら\nここまでムキにはなりません",
      "startTime": 43.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "でも彼女は言ったんです。「サニーピースなんて\n大した実力もないくせに」って……",
      "startTime": 50.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "みんなを侮辱することは私が許しません\n私がアイドルの道を選んだことは……",
      "startTime": 57.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "……サニーピースの一員になったことは\n間違いじゃないと証明したいんです！",
      "startTime": 62.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（自分への暴言よりも）\n（サニピを悪く言われたことが許せないのか……）",
      "startTime": 67.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "お願いします！　仕事に穴は開けません\nみんなには迷惑は掛けないので、出場させて下さい！",
      "startTime": 74.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……分かった。スケジュールは俺の方で調整しておくよ",
      "startTime": 80.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "怜にとっても挑戦することで得られるものがあるはずだ\nいい結果を期待しているぞ",
      "startTime": 90.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　サニーピースとして\n恥ずかしくないパフォーマンスをしてみせます！",
      "startTime": 95.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "startTime": 99.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-02-000-evening",
      "startTime": 100.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ダンス大会で踊るのは久しぶりのはずだが\n……さすがだな",
      "startTime": 105.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "はぁはぁ……まだまだ、もっと練習しないと……",
      "startTime": 108.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに無理しなくても\n今のままで十分上位を狙えるんじゃないか？",
      "startTime": 119.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "上位入賞じゃダメです。優勝候補のエリカに勝たないと\n彼女を納得させられません",
      "startTime": 127.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "私にはブランクがあるので、今はとにかく練習して\n少しでも勘を取り戻さないと……",
      "startTime": 134.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ブランクなんてまるで感じなかったが\n怜は納得していないのか？",
      "startTime": 139.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルになってからも、いろんなジャンルのダンスに\n挑戦していたので、体は動けていると思います",
      "startTime": 145.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-rei015.m4a",
      "text": "でも何かが違う気がして……\n踊っていてしっくりこないんです",
      "startTime": 153.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-rei016.m4a",
      "text": "だから沢山練習して、以前はどんな風に踊っていたか\n早く思い出したいんです",
      "startTime": 161.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-rei017.m4a",
      "text": "お願いします、納得がいくまでやらせて下さい！",
      "startTime": 163.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "……分かった。だが無茶はするな\n水分と休憩はこまめにとること。いいな？",
      "startTime": 171.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-rei018.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　ありがとうございます！",
      "startTime": 174.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "（気合いが入っているのはいいが）\n（オーバーワークにならないか心配だな……）",
      "startTime": 180.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "startTime": 184.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-02-000-night",
      "startTime": 185.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "夜になってもスタジオの明かりが点いているから\n心配になって来てみれば……",
      "startTime": 190.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-rei019.m4a",
      "text": "はあ、はあ……もっと踊って勘を取り戻さないと……\nもっと、もっと……",
      "startTime": 203.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-rei020.m4a",
      "text": "はあ、はあ……あ、{user}さん\nどうしたんですか？",
      "startTime": 215,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたのかじゃない。無茶はするなと言ったはずだ\n今日はもう終わりにして帰るんだ",
      "startTime": 221.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-rei021.m4a",
      "text": "待って下さい。もう少しだけ練習させて下さい",
      "startTime": 223.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "そう言って、毎日居残り練習しているじゃないか\nまだ自分のダンスに納得がいかないのか？",
      "startTime": 232.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-rei022.m4a",
      "text": "はい……うまく説明出来ないんですが\n何かが違う気がするんです",
      "startTime": 241.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-rei023.m4a",
      "text": "以前はこのやり方で優勝したのに\nどうしても違和感が消えないんです",
      "startTime": 247.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-rei024.m4a",
      "text": "何か大事なことを見落としている気がするんです",
      "startTime": 250.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "違和感か……\n確かに、いつもの怜らしくない気はするな",
      "startTime": 257.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-rei025.m4a",
      "text": "私らしくない……？",
      "startTime": 260.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "俺には、今の怜は息苦しそうに見える",
      "startTime": 263.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "サニピで踊っている怜は、もっと生き生きして\n見ていてワクワクする華やかさがあった",
      "startTime": 270.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-rei026.m4a",
      "text": "今の私は息苦しい……\nでも、練習が苦しいのは当然ですよね？",
      "startTime": 277.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-rei027.m4a",
      "text": "大会で勝つには辛い練習に耐えて\n高いスキルを身につけるべきだと思うんですが",
      "startTime": 285.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-koh018.m4a",
      "text": "技術の優劣を競うのならそれでいいのかもしれない\nだが怜は、なんのために大会に出場するんだ？",
      "startTime": 294.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-rei028.m4a",
      "text": "……アイドルを馬鹿にしたエリカに\nアイドルの凄さを見せるためです",
      "startTime": 300.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-koh019.m4a",
      "text": "それなら無理して昔のスタイルに戻さなくても\nいいんじゃないか？",
      "startTime": 306.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-koh020.m4a",
      "text": "ダンサーだった昔に戻るんじゃなくて\nアイドルになった今の怜で踊ればいいんだ",
      "startTime": 310.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-rei029.m4a",
      "text": "今のまま……アイドルの私で……",
      "startTime": 314.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-rei030.m4a",
      "text": "……私、勝つことばかり考えて\n大事なことを忘れていました",
      "startTime": 322.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-rei031.m4a",
      "text": "私はエリカにアイドルの素晴らしさを伝えたい……",
      "startTime": 324.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-rei032.m4a",
      "text": "そのためには『アイドル・一ノ瀬怜』として\nステージに立たなければいけなかったんですね",
      "startTime": 333.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-rei033.m4a",
      "text": "感じていた違和感の正体がやっと分かりました\n私はアイドルとして優勝してみせます！",
      "startTime": 340.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-rei034.m4a",
      "text": "そうと決まればアイドルらしいダンス構成に変更を……\nそうだ！　大会でサニピの曲を使ってもいいですか？",
      "startTime": 349.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-koh021.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、もちろん構わないよ",
      "startTime": 354.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-rei035.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます！　みんなと一緒の気分なら\nどんな相手にも負ける気がしません！",
      "startTime": 362.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_02-koh022.m4a",
      "text": "（晴れやかないい笑顔だ。アイドル・一ノ瀬怜が）\n（どんなパフォーマンスを見せてくれるのか楽しみだな）",
      "startTime": 369.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}